### How to Use

1Ô∏è‚É£ Run the program and choose an option from the menu:

Welcome to our Vole Machine
1) Read file and load program
2) Execute program
3) Display Data
4) Exit
Enter your choice: 

2Ô∏è‚É£ To load a program, enter a valid text file name.
3Ô∏è‚É£ To execute the program, select option 2.
4Ô∏è‚É£ To view machine memory, choose option 3.

Example Program File (commands.txt):
2001
2102
2203
2304
